    public class TrueNTHAccessToken
extends TrueNTHToken
    TrueNTH access token model.

    Immutable after construction.

    Expected format(JSon):
    {
    "access_token": "string",
    "expires_in": number,
    "refresh_token": "string",
    "scope": "string",
    "token_type": "string"
    }

    {
    "access_token": "lRk6RTR",
    "token_type": "Bearer",
    "expires_in": 3600,
    "refresh_token": "beKTdy",
    "scope": "email"
    }

    Since:
    Oct 22, 2015
    Author:
    Victor de Lima Soares

        Constructor.
        Parameters:
        token - Token string.
        expiresIn - Token expiration time, after creation.
        refreshToken - Token to be used when this token is no longer valid.
        scope - Scope to which this token is valid.
        tokenType - Token type. This parameter should be a string representation of one of constants defined in TrueNTHTokenType.
